# Personal Financial Context

This file is injected into every AI analysis prompt as background context about how your
finances are structured. Copy it to context.md (gitignored) and fill in your own details.

---

## Income

- Describe your income sources and any patterns that might look unusual (e.g. split payroll
  deposits, freelance payments, irregular amounts).

## Account Structure

- Describe which accounts are for operating/spending vs. holding/savings.
- Note any internal transfer patterns that should NOT be counted as income or expenses
  (e.g. vault movements, cross-account shuffles, credit card payments).

## Recurring / Expected Charges

- List any charges that appear multiple times per billing cycle and are expected
  (e.g. usage-based API billing, split subscription charges).

## Investments

- Note any transfers that are investment contributions and should not be treated as expenses.
